{"tid":452571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(腳疣)想做冷凍治療 去邊間好?","createTime":"2017-10-30T10:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T18:38:42.000Z","uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6255ff8ceccd64010d95e569b713e0bb7c1f6c","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"有粒腳疣跟左幾年 愈黎愈大愈黎愈痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想做冷凍治療殺撚左去 想問邊間好 同埋大約幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe01b0f89e1c940377de1abf00d7e91d30b7d84","tid":452571,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.mhs.hk/m/STD.html#std\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhs.hk%2Fm%2FSTD.html%23std&d=jpN7jgqLyokpm27jydmuRXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d77862b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mhs.hk/m/STD.html#std</a>"},{"pid":"f96c403dc1a295295e4a22ec6df76baefcaac586","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.mhs.hk/m/STD.html#std\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhs.hk%2Fm%2FSTD.html%23std&d=jpN7jgqLyokpm27jydmuRXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d77862b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mhs.hk/m/STD.html#std</a></blockquote><br />\nJJ先咁貴姐 手腳聽講500左右就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d762348d689760f913439624a054698386ed0ce9","tid":452571,"uid":146245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"幾大粒呀，當年我就咁去疹所用辣雞燒兩野，400搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e56816fdedb382b7f19b6ca6e58cbb602f3abd","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾大粒呀，當年我就咁去疹所用辣雞燒兩野，400搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直經0.5~0.6cm姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以比你做個間嘅地址我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e04021c9e2a4a24b14888b8afda360a92eea28","tid":452571,"uid":146245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾大粒呀，當年我就咁去疹所用辣雞燒兩野，400搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直經0.5~0.6cm姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以比你做個間嘅地址我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗一般疹所都會有，不過打針落腳趾好痛"},{"pid":"2939d79e270da94a9244674c965b09a7f86ecf2f","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾大粒呀，當年我就咁去疹所用辣雞燒兩野，400搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直經0.5~0.6cm姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以比你做個間嘅地址我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗一般疹所都會有，不過打針落腳趾好痛</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b583b7eecb959b3069fd408c4017fad6b868132","tid":452571,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"冷凍好易翻發 用辣雞啦 <br />\n反正腳無人睇到"},{"pid":"0c77d5a802b1e11242ae67df801ad3686af66117","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://skin22.com/form/GO0001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskin22.com%2Fform%2FGO0001&d=jpN7jgqLyokpm27jydmuRXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a545e2b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://skin22.com/form/GO0001</a><br />\n<br />\n想試下呢間用激光 會唔會有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af01904001d07f09890794153750446d2a5b96f5","tid":452571,"uid":79839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"求圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68e3bc25230a6808b0897b577a139363f383a6b","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80fcb04635d8f8c07a9623ee39d254d6739e1aa","tid":452571,"uid":98172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>求圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n Jed, thanks. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff46ed6600432d3d05b1a80cf0b8a48096577476","tid":452571,"uid":79839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>求圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67aa9952e973dba989f161868cbc96f10dfc28c","tid":452571,"uid":93218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"腳板本來好靚,可惜有粒野"},{"pid":"3456a720912acae408df8daa023beadfa34983b6","tid":452571,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"有冇試過用salicylic acid? 我之前連續用左兩個禮拜左右就斷左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然要好耐，但佢效果好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6a84a9470dc3ab2b8cb2f8beedb9458113ede4","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過用salicylic acid? 我之前連續用左兩個禮拜左右就斷左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然要好耐，但佢效果好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊要唔要自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a39cba22f5a887e03e535fb57532342c36c7b07","tid":452571,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過用salicylic acid? 我之前連續用左兩個禮拜左右就斷左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然要好耐，但佢效果好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊要唔要自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過嗰啲講到自己好有效一次就可以斷尾嘅(賣成差唔多5舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )freezer 黎自己搞，點知完全冇用，過幾日又生番。<br />\n<br />\n之後買左支salicylic acid stick 黎自己擦，keep住日日擦，擦左兩個禮拜左右就冇左，到而家差唔多兩年都未復發過。最重要係支野先70蚊左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b890ac8a98c4acfa8c18731f1b7a50f174264c40","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過用salicylic acid? 我之前連續用左兩個禮拜左右就斷左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然要好耐，但佢效果好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊要唔要自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過嗰啲講到自己好有效一次就可以斷尾嘅(賣成差唔多5舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )freezer 黎自己搞，點知完全冇用，過幾日又生番。<br />\n<br />\n之後買左支salicylic acid stick 黎自己擦，keep住日日擦，擦左兩個禮拜左右就冇左，到而家差唔多兩年都未復發過。<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係支野先70蚊左右</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日狗沖買"},{"pid":"ebdbf725ba4d261861597db28429daad5e54a5b3","tid":452571,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:03:43.000Z","msg":"細個生過 又係好似你咁大粒 <br />\n最後排公立排左成年先有得冷凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n街買個d藥水同freezer都冇用 因為生得太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後凍左幾次 出大大水泡就好返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f573446af4b75a8117f7d8d4aff604c179ba081b","tid":452571,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:10:22.000Z","msg":"之前隻腳好多，而且生左好多年，因為細個唔識野以為係&lsquo;&rsquo;枕&lsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n之後買左之藍白色盒唔知咩酸日日搽<br />\n有一日去搣佢，成塊比我搣甩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家起碼都2年冇返發"},{"pid":"f76e60096c97c8b8d341824a0f1839ab8f609311","tid":452571,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過用salicylic acid? 我之前連續用左兩個禮拜左右就斷左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然要好耐，但佢效果好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊要唔要自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過嗰啲講到自己好有效一次就可以斷尾嘅(賣成差唔多5舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )freezer 黎自己搞，點知完全冇用，過幾日又生番。<br />\n<br />\n之後買左支salicylic acid stick 黎自己擦，keep住日日擦，擦左兩個禮拜左右就冇左，到而家差唔多兩年都未復發過。<span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係支野先70蚊左右</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日狗沖買</blockquote><br />\n我用嗰支野叫wart-off stick <br />\n喺澳洲買嘅 $11澳紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港可能平d<br />\n香港唔知有冇同一隻牌子，冇過成份一樣就得! Salicylic acid 40% w/w<br />\n<br />\n你日日擦，擦完用防水膠布貼住(唔好俾個位接觸空氣)。到第二日沖涼前&quot;meet&quot;左佢，沖涼嗰陣洗乾淨，沖完抹乾再擦過再貼過，直到d疣冇左同回復正常皮膚就停得。每個人唔同，可能要到3~4個禮拜先會完全好番晒，不過你會睇得有進展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你嗰個位有剌痛同紅腫得好西利就唔好擦住，等d symptoms 冇左再繼續擦。"},{"pid":"1af28fe6492dbb9ccfdcc2188effe657de22a78d","tid":452571,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6368af497c5d8eb033bd8b0865ace2c806db5311","tid":452571,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ad2235cb1540b7cdcb2aa2e288d8e82ed7cb77","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢支搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我買左呢種試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ZZ7xvs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0ZZ7xvs.jpg&h=91e1ffd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06e1e80af4c73c46826dafd0af1dc86d7380bcf5","tid":452571,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:47:25.000Z","msg":"其實成因係點，無喇喇生一粒出黎"},{"pid":"51ddd820bb9de9591b00b44922365e5d6b0d6282","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實成因係點，無喇喇生一粒出黎</blockquote><br />\n皮膚病黎 會傳染<br />\n多數係公共地方 多水嘅<br />\n如公共游泳池果D<br />\n<br />\n但我第一粒真係唔知點黎 果陣返機場推行李<br />\n返返下就生左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caf5f92a6f1edf8e52e6b3632620e382d8aa080","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20693d04e233967d587bcbd323c56996caace28","tid":452571,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要keep住擦到嗰個皮膚回復正常膚質先好停"},{"pid":"eb58439d102537a4192ea54f59149e5f0dd5726b","tid":452571,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T07:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要keep住擦到嗰個皮膚回復正常膚質先好停</blockquote><br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e621f224ab8a1e44fea992fed32c0c87b10a0532","tid":452571,"uid":44070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要keep住擦到嗰個皮膚回復正常膚質先好停</blockquote><br />\n收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就快好㗎啦，加油，我知行路痛撚到仆街，生哩粒樣真係好撚痛苦<img src=\"/as